<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I kuong un gamnuom lam chuh zuon hen,
 Kinepna lawngpuon zak zelin;
 I guol ei na ngak haw gel zingin,
 Zie mun chuh I tun tieng chawl tai tiu.

[V2]
 Mitthi hul tieng kipaka kikhawm ding,
 Sepgim na beih tieng leh chawldam tai tiu;
 Tatsate'n kipah la a sak u chuh zai tiu,
 Nunnuomte umna In a kikhawm in.

[V3]
 2. I kuong un gamnuom lam chuh zuon hen,
 Lau lo hielin chieh zel hitiu;
 Lungmuon na kuong chawlhmun I naih tieng,
 Zie chawlhna mun vak chuh mu taitiu.

[V4]
 3. Gam nuoma tang hawih leh vak nuom chuh,
 Pakcha hawih chitin in a bawm;
 Ziechun ei Tanpa leh hehpihpa,
 Chawian in kipahna la sai tiu.

[V5]
 4. Gam nuom apat chun huihchim a nung,
 Zie a zing khawvak hawih achun;
 I hehpihteu tawh kituok hitiu,
 Lungkham thih leh natna bei ta'n a.</lyrics>
<title>GATHERINGAFTER TEARS</title>
<hymn_number>396</hymn_number>
</song>